gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 135, Lakers 119
gameRecap.excerpt: The Rockets defeated the Lakers, 135-119. Jalen Green led the way with 34 points, a career-high 12 rebounds, and seven assists for the Rockets, with Alperen Sengun adding 31 points, 12 rebounds, and seven assists in the victory. LeBron James tallied 23 points, 10 assists, and six rebounds for the Lakers in the losing effort. The Rockets improve to 22-24, while the Lakers fall to 24-24.
